# SMARTIE
**Molecular Neuroscience Lab**

**Machine-learning pipeline for predicting RNA-binding protein (RBP) targets from TRIBE and STAMP editing data.**

TRIBE (Targets of RNA-Binding Proteins Identified By Editing) and STAMP (Surveying Targets by APOBEC-Mediated Profiling) fuse an RBP to a base-editing enzyme (ADAR or APOBEC). Sites edited above background identify where the RBP binds. `smartie` automates the full analysis: loading raw editing files, engineering 18 biologically motivated features, training a Random Forest classifier, and generating publication-quality plots.

